# ğŸ”¥ MUST-REMEMBER PATTERNS

| Problem              | Technique      |
| -------------------- | -------------- |
| Max subarray sum     | Kadane         |
| Count subarrays      | Prefix + map   |
| Fixed sum (positive) | Sliding window |
| All subarray sum     | Math formula   |
| Longest subarray     | Prefix + map   |

